34:22.360 --> 34:24.560
that Wayland is meant to give you

34:24.560 --> 34:29.000
by having to rely on X in terms of security and so on.

34:29.000 --> 34:32.120
So yeah, we invested in making sure

34:32.120 --> 34:34.760
