34:34.760 --> 34:37.560
And I think it's actually worth mentioning that I think

34:37.560 --> 34:39.760
for the last five years at least,

34:39.760 --> 34:41.800
Red Hat has more or less single-handedly maintained

34:41.800 --> 34:43.840
